==Plan==

====The United States Federal Government should end restrictions that allow the Secretary of the Interior to block production of wind and/or solar energy in Tribal Energy Resource Agreements.  ====


====Legal frames and stereotypes force American Indians to internalize two equally dangerous representations – that of the &amp;#34;noble savage&amp;#34; and as &amp;#34;fierce savage&amp;#34; who owns casinos – these images pre-frame decision making vis-a-vie American Indians. ====
